title: Otokonoko no Koto wa Nanimo Shiranai
original_name: 男の子のことは何も知らない
sinopse:
1-2. Otokonoko no Koto wa Nanimo Shiranai (I have no idea about boys)
3-4. Shinshi wa Kedamono ga Osuki (The Gentleman and the Beast) 5. Ai kamo Shirenee daro! (Could this be Love) 6. Furachi na Yoru ni (A Regrettable Night)
